Focal Length: 85mm (a common portrait lens focal length, flattering for faces)
White Balance: Daylight or Custom (to accurately represent skin tones and colors)
Lighting: Softbox lighting from the front-right, with a fill light or reflector on the left to soften shadows. Please use the facial features and structure of the attached image and hairstyle. Do not change the face. Make it look real.""" ;
