pkgc:ID_519742648 a skos:Concept ;
    dc:date "2025-02-07"^^xsd:date ;
    skos:prefLabel """AGIS Office Address is

4 Peace Drive
Central Area, Abuja FCT

Hours
Monday—Friday: 9:00AM–3:00PM



Each Map costs 5k. Here are the maps we need.

1. Land-use MAP
2. SAT-IMAGE MAP
3. Cadastral MAP
4. FCC Overview MAP
5. FCT MAP
6. Infrastructure MAP

NOTE:
1. All Payments are to be made in the following Banks (Request and fill AGIS customized teller);

Zenith bank
Fidelity bank
First bank
Eco bank
Heritage bank
SunTrust Savings & Loans Ltd
2. Present a copy of your bank teller at the finance desk at AGIS office, and obtain AGIS receipt

3. Submit a copy of your AGIS receipt at MAP Production desk in the front office (ask customer care for direction) and collect your requested MAP in less than an hour.""" ;
    pkg:sourceMap "life.mm" .

