pkgc:ID_879790714 a skos:Concept ;
    dc:date "2025-04-09"^^xsd:date ;
    skos:prefLabel "As a systems engineer at bed bath and beyond, I led on shore and offshore teams of engineers in delivering a new loyalty application, and upgrading the infrastructure it was built on from on-premise to cloud to improve it's capacity during peak retail periods. I used an iterative approach to deliver value incrementally, while testing capacity at identified bottlenecks. I also created a microsite in sharepoint to house key system knowledge in documentation and controls for offshore engineers to troubleshoot issues on their own." ;
    pkg:sourceMap "life.mm" .

